<p>
	To achieve the same design for the testimonial widget as on our demo page you have to click on <b>Layout</b> tab and set the <b>Bottom Margin</b> to <b>90</b>px, <b>Padding</b> to <b>10, 0, 0, 0</b>px and the <b>Row Layout</b> to <b>Full Width Stretched</b>. Then click on the <b>Design</b> tab and set the <b>Background Color</b> to <b>#2e3b4e</b>.
